triśaraṇagamanam buddhadharmasaṃghānām āśrayaṇīyatvena cetobhajanam | yācanā buddhānām aparinirvāṇena saṃsārāvasthanārthaṃ vacanaviśeṣaḥ | adhyeṣaṇā buddhānām anavaratavad dharmadeśanārthaṃ cākṣaviśeṣodīraṇam | ātmaniryātanaṃ sarvabuddhabodhisattvebhya ātmadehaniryātanam | puṇyapariṇāmam | etat kriyākalāpaprasūtasya puṇyasya sarvasattvānāṃ buddhatvāya niryātanam ||
